description: Fuel tank inspected for contamination. Drained and refilled with clean fuel. No debris found.
Emergency exit doors inspected. Lubricated seals and confirmed proper locking mechanism operation.
Oxygen system inspected and refilled. No leaks detected in tubing or connectors.
Repaired loose wiring in navigation system. Conducted functional test, system operational.
Adjusted flap actuators due to asymmetrical deployment. Ground test confirmed proper movement.
Autopilot recalibrated after reported altitude hold issues. System tested and verified.
